{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"十唱“十六条”——欢呼中共中央关于无产阶级文化大革命的决定","authors":["左正　赵凌龙　毛佩琦","魏凯　赵先勋"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":8,"day":12}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"十唱“十六条”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——欢呼中共中央关于无产阶级文化大革命的决定"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民大学学生  左正　赵凌龙　毛佩琦  魏凯　赵先勋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一唱“十六条”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“十六条”订得好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想放光芒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一轮红日心头照。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二唱“十六条”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的新文告，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一斗二批又三改，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命重担肩上挑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三唱“十六条”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四大武器掌握牢："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大鸣大放大辩论，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有革命的大字报。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四唱“十六条”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发动群众最重要，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“敢”字当头去战斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛鬼蛇神全扫掉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五唱“十六条”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级路线贯彻好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团结群众大多数，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的政策要记牢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六唱“十六条”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两类矛盾区分好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命同志手挽手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共同对敌心一条。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七唱“十六条”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢呼群众的新创造："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化革命委员会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朵朵红花永不凋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八唱“十六条”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改革旧文教，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学制要短课要简，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砸烂资产阶级的老一套。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九唱“十六条”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思想革命化要做到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抓革命来促生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多快好省掀高潮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十唱“十六条”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命凯歌震云霄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远跟着毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命红旗举得高！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"革命委员会","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}